    <string name="guide_step1_title">1. Login or Register</string>
    <string name="guide_step1_content">To use all features, you need to log in. From the main screen, tap \'Login\' or \'Register\' to create a new account.</string>
    <string name="guide_step2_title">2. Add a New Event</string>
    <string name="guide_step2_content">Tap the \'+\' icon or the \'Add Event\' option from the bottom navigation. Enter the event name, date, time, and save.</string>
    <string name="guide_step3_title">3. View Countdown</string>
    <string name="guide_step3_content">Return to the main screen to see a list of events with their countdown timers updated automatically.</string>
    <string name="guide_step4_title">4. Edit or Delete Events</string>
    <string name="guide_step4_content">Tap the settings icon on an event card to edit or delete it. You can also add notes if needed.</string>
    <string name="guide_step5_title">5. Customize the App</string>
    <string name="guide_step5_content">From the \'Settings\' screen, you can change the language, theme, or back up event data.</string>

